<dl id="n05167a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05167a">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05167a"> 167(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ every murder is perverse</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Les suicides sans d&eacute;sespoir et les <mark>homicides sans remords</mark> ouvrent parfois la sc&egrave;ne morbide. Les fugues sont souvent les premiers signes r&eacute;v&eacute;lateurs de la d&eacute;mence. <font color="green">[Suicide without despair and homicide without remorse sometimes open the morbid scene. Fugues are often the first tell-tale signs of dementia.]</font> <small> Dr. Constanza Pascal, <a name="OMAD" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#OMAD"><cite title="source">La d&eacute;mence pr&eacute;coce</cite></a> (1911) 167</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
